The '''Agr''' was a model of [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] named after an [[Agr|animal]] indigenous to [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. It was designed and optimized for atmospheric flight, but could also engage in [[Starfighter combat/Legends|dogfights]] in [[Realspace/Legends|space]]. It was the predecessor of the [[Agr (starfighter)|Fast Agr]].

